'''飓风卡特里娜'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Katrina}}）是一场形成日期较晚的[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，也是[[1981年大西洋飓风季|1981年大西洋飓风季]]第11场获命名的风暴和第七场飓风，于1981年11月袭击[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]和[[大安的列斯群岛|大安的列斯群岛]]部分地区。气旋源自11月3日西[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]的[[热带扰动|扰动天气区]]，起初增强速度缓慢，于11月5日升级成热带风暴并获名“卡特里娜”。约六小时后，风暴达到[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]每小时140公里的最高强度。气旋于11月6日清晨沿古巴[[卡马圭省|卡马圭省]]南岸[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]，然后快速减弱成热带风暴，并于数小时后进入大西洋。卡特里娜接下来加速向东北移动，于11月6日晚经过巴哈马，再于11月7日同[[锋_(气象)|锋面天气系统]]合并后不久完全消散。

[[大开曼|大开曼]]出现[[海龙卷风|海龙卷风]]，将一棵[[海葡萄|葡萄树]]扯断并砸入布拉奇礁酒店的酒吧。古巴降下暴雨，最高降雨量达400毫米。受此影响，该国山区在风暴经过期间爆发山洪。卡马圭省南部有多座桥梁和多条铁路被冲毁，另有两家制糖厂受损。估计有4641户民居遭受破坏，其中39套毁于一旦。此外，约有80%的甘蔗作物受损。卡马圭省有两人在试图渡过暴涨的河流时溺毙。巴哈马降下360毫米雨量，包括[[西瓜|西瓜]]、[[西红柿|西红柿]]和[[玉米|玉米]]在内的农作物受损，其中又以[[长岛_(巴哈马)|长岛]]灾情最为严重。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Katrina 1981 track.png}}
1981年11月1日，西加勒比海发展出由大范围云系和雷暴带组成的[[热带扰动|扰动天气区]]，随后又开始形成[[低气压|低气压区]]。11月3日清晨，气象机构把位于[[开曼群岛|开曼群岛]]以南约240公里海域的天气系统归类成热带低气压。<ref name="MWR">{{cite report | author1 = Miles B. Lawrence | author2 = Joseph M. Pelissier | title = Atlantic Hurricane Season of 1981 | publisher = [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]]; Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | date = 1982-07 | work = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | accessdate = 2016-10-25 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1981.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131126081006/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1981.pdf | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | page = 864 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-11-26 }}</ref>[[国家飓风中心|国家飓风中心]]在当时的实际操作中于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]11月3日晚22点开始针对气旋发布公告。首份公告中判断热带低气压的增强速度缓慢，但[[对流|对流]]强劲，所以估计会在24小时内达到热带风暴标准。<ref>{{cite report | author = Robert C. Sheets | title = Tropical Depression Discussion Depression Number 17 | date = 1981-11-03 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-25 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | format = [[JPEG|JPG]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304051608/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0141-jpg/1981/atlantic/katrina/tropdisc/tcd11032100z.jpg | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0141-jpg/1981/atlantic/katrina/tropdisc/tcd11032100z.jpg }}</ref>。11月4日清晨，气旋依然杂乱无章，卫星图像和加勒比海多间气象站的观测结果都表明低气压没有强化<ref>{{cite report | author = Robert C. Sheets | title = Tropical Depression Discussion Depression Number 17 | date = 1981-11-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304081747/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0141-jpg/1981/atlantic/katrina/tropdisc/tcd11040300z.jpg | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-25 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | format = JPG | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0141-jpg/1981/atlantic/katrina/tropdisc/tcd11040300z.jpg }}</ref>。不过，仅过了数小时，气旋就在向北飘移期间升级成热带风暴并获名“卡特里娜”（{{lang|en|Katrina}}）<ref name="TCR">{{cite report | author = Miles B. Lawrence | title = Hurricane Katrina Preliminary Report | date = 1981-11-30 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-25 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0141-jpg/1981/atlantic/katrina/prenhc/prelim_katrina_1103-1107.01.jpg | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304055740/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0141-jpg/1981/atlantic/katrina/prenhc/prelim_katrina_1103-1107.01.jpg | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | format = JPG }}</ref>。

风暴继续增强并缓慢转向[[罗盘方位|东北偏北]]，之后又转朝东北移动<ref name="TCR" />。但在[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]]侦察机确认气旋内的风暴达到热带风暴强度后，美国国家飓风中心才于{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}11月4日下午16点把气旋归类成热带低气压<ref>{{cite report | author = Robert C. Sheets | title = Tropical Cyclone Discussion Tropical Storm Katrina | date = 1981-11-04 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-25 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | format = JPG | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304214929/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0141-jpg/1981/atlantic/katrina/tropdisc/tcd11041500z.jpg | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0141-jpg/1981/atlantic/katrina/tropdisc/tcd11041500z.jpg }}</ref>。{{lang|en|UTC}}11月5日早上6点，卡特里娜的强度达到[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下的一级飓风标准<ref name="TCR" />。侦察机于当天测得980[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，29[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最低[[气压|气压]]，地面观测结果显示风暴的[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]达到每小时140公里，这也是卡特里娜的最高强度<ref name="MWR" />。接下来飓风在逼近古巴期间略有减弱，于11月6日以风力时速120公里强度[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]该国[[卡马圭省|卡马圭省]]。进入陆地上空后不久，气旋减弱成热带风暴<ref name="TCR" />。受[[美国东岸|美国东岸]]近海的[[低压槽|低压槽]]逐渐增强影响，卡特里娜加速向东北偏东前进<ref>{{cite report | author = Gilbert B. Clark | title = Tropical Cyclone Discussion Hurricane Katrina | date = 1981-11-06 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-25 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | format = JPG | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304084509/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0141-jpg/1981/atlantic/katrina/tropdisc/tcd11060900z.jpg | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0141-jpg/1981/atlantic/katrina/tropdisc/tcd11060900z.jpg }}</ref>。到了{{lang|en|UTC}}11月6日下午13点30分，风暴已进入大西洋<ref>{{cite report | author = Neil L. Frank | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131216172329/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0141-jpg/1981/atlantic/katrina/tropdisc/tcd11061330z.jpg | title = Tropical Cyclone Discussion Hurricane Katrina | date = 1981-11-06 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-25 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0141-jpg/1981/atlantic/katrina/tropdisc/tcd11061330z.jpg | format = JPG | archivedate = 2013-12-16 }}</ref>。当晚，卡特里娜在穿越巴哈马中部期间缓慢减弱，之后侦察机已无法定位闭合环流，气旋于11月7日晚在[[百慕大|百慕大]]东南偏南方向约610公里洋面消散<ref name="TCR" />。

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
[[File:Hurricane_Katrina_(1981).JPG|thumb]]

据哈瓦那电台消息，面对卡特里娜来袭，古巴中部有15万人和12万头牛转移<ref name="AM" />，古巴民防官员向五个省发出风暴预警<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | title = Katrina Losing Punch | date = 1981-11-06 | newspaper = Indiana Gazette}}</ref>。巴哈马中部和东部进入[[热带气旋警告|飓风观察预警]]生效状态<ref name="NEWS1">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | title = Hurricane Katrina near Cuban Coast | date = 1981-11-06 | newspaper = Daily Herald}}</ref>。有关部门建议[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]东南沿海地区的小型船只留在港口附近，不过气象机构预测气旋不会对美国构成威胁，之后的实际情况也确实如此<ref name="tdh">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | title = Hurricane Hits Cuba, Weakly | date = 1981-11-06 | publisher = Tyrone Daily Herald}}</ref><ref name="TCR" />。

开曼群岛各地的降雨量普遍达到300毫米<ref name="AM">{{cite news | title = November 6, 1981, Friday, AM cycle | author = Staff Writer | date = 1981-11-06 | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]]}}</ref>。[[大开曼|大开曼]]出现[[海龙卷风|海龙卷风]]，将一棵[[海葡萄|葡萄树]]扯断，砸入布拉奇礁酒店的酒吧<ref name="TCR" />。古巴的最高降雨量达400毫米，24小时最高降雨量也有331毫米<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.hidro.cu/hidrologia1.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131105222344/http://www.hidro.cu/hidrologia1.htm | title = Principales Eventos Pluviales Sobre Cuba En El Periodo 1963 - 2006 | date = 2006 | work = CubAgua | publisher = Instituto Nacional de Recursos Hidráulicos | accessdate = 2013-11-05 | archivedate = 2013-11-05 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。受此影响，该国山区在风暴经过期间爆发山洪<ref name="NEWS2">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | title = Katrina losing her punch | newspaper = Syracuse Herald-Journal | date = 1981-11-06}}</ref>。卡马圭省南部有多座桥梁和多条铁路被冲毁，另有两家制糖厂受损。估计有4641户民居遭受破坏，其中39套毁于一旦。此外，约有80%的甘蔗作物受损。<ref>{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304120018/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0141-jpg/1981/atlantic/katrina/postevent/report_havana1109.jpg | accessdate = 2016-10-25 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0141-jpg/1981/atlantic/katrina/postevent/report_havana1109.jpg | title = Hurricane Katrina Passes Over Cuba | author = Tipton | date = 1981-11-16 | work = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Washington, D.C. | format = JPG }}</ref>卡马圭省有两人在试图渡过暴涨的河流时溺毙<ref name="AM" />。巴哈马降下360毫米雨量，虽然没有人员伤亡，但群岛中部降下的暴雨还是导致[[长岛_(巴哈马)|长岛]]的西瓜、西红柿和玉米作物受损<ref name="NEWS3">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | title = Katrina fizzles out after destructive run | newspaper = Syracuse Herald-Journal | date = 1981-11-10}}</ref>。受风暴造成的恶劣天气影响，本森与何吉金杯板球赛第15场比赛被迫取消<ref name="News4">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | title = Why did the promoters wait until Saturday to inform the public? | newspaper = The Daily Gleaner | date = 1981-11-10}}</ref>。

